Name: Average time from 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' to 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average time to complete 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' after 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time for 'SW-Checklist Completed' after 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time taken for 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the end of the case

Name: Time difference between 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' for cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' follows
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' before 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' in cases leading to 'SW-EIC Major Revision'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' in the fastest case to reach 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in reverse sequence cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Time from 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to 'SW-EIC Accept' in successful submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time for 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' grouped by 'performer' to identify efficiency differences
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and the end of case grouped by the last value of performer

Name: Total time for 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' across all cases where 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded' did not follow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and the end of case where activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded does not occur

Name: Total time from 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' in variants where 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit' occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
